title: Farberware FMO09BLKSS Countertop 900 Watts Microwave Oven with Child Lock-Perfect for Apartments and Dorms-Easy Clean Grey Interior, 0.9 Cu. Ft, Black Stainless
description: This countertop microwave is the perfect size for office break rooms or home kitchens. With one-touch cooking programs, you can quickly prepare six of the most popular food items at the press of a button. Choose from 10 power levels up to 900 watts for precision cooking. The large digital display features a clock and countdown timer, so you can easily track cooking progress. The memory function allows you to save and customize your favorite settings for convenience. Designed with a large door, it includes an easy-grip handle and a child safety lock for added security.
